				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">I was very supprised with the number of positive posts from sorcerers with respect to these new realm abilities.  I think some of the last few posters have realized what they really mean to us.
<br />

<br />
I would not call it "whining" when many of us express concerns with what Mythic is proposing here.  With the Purge and Group Purge and Determination Abilities, our Crowd control will be completely disabled in RvR.  Furthermore, our mezzing ability is the only thing standing between us and a 1 hit death in many cases.
<br />

<br />
Everyone hates being mezzed, I do too.  These will be the realm abilities everyone will be spending their realm levels on.  With our limited nuking ability (especially if you are a mind sorceror) we will be next to useless in RvR.
<br />

<br />
I seriously hope Mythic reconsiders this one.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
